<paragraph blockId="47.[151,1437,1401,2037]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,453,1545,1570]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="47" pageNumber="48" reason="1">General distribution.</emphasis>
Endemic: Northern Persian Gulf, including 
<collectingCountry box="[965,1050,1545,1569]" name="Kuwait" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Kuwait</collectingCountry>
