<collectingCountry box="[580,625,1582,1605]" name="Iraq" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">Iraq</collectingCountry>
will be reported in future.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="47.[151,1437,1401,2037]" box="[199,501,1617,1642]" pageId="47" pageNumber="48">
